1157788943.text: "The knock-down of the ATP binding cassette transporters A1 (ABCA1), G1 (ABCG1), and of the scavenger receptor-BI (SR-BI) diminishes but does not completely block the transport of apoA-I or HDL, so that other receptors appear to be involved."
